Proud to celebrate an outstanding performance of the Amherst College team‚ÄîAndreas Rasvanis, Sherry Jiang, and Claudiu Babin‚Äîat the 2024 ICPC Northeast Regional this past Sunday! Competing on-site against 105 teams from universities across New England and five Canadian provinces, our team took 1st place among undergraduate institutions and 16th place overall, solving 8 out of 13 problems. A huge thank you to the organizers and sponsors for making this event possible, as well as to the Amherst CS department for their invaluable support.
